h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Catalog highlights</h4><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>FABRIC: Stay cool and stylish with our Trucker Mesh Cap, crafted from a comfortable poly/cotton blend. Featuring breathable trucker mesh panels, this cap combines durability with airflow for a relaxed fit in any setting.</li><li>MID PROFILE/PRO-MODEL: Elevate your game with our mid-profile, pro-model cap. Designed for performance and style, this cap features a structured build that offers a comfortable fit and a professional look.</li><li>VISOR: Enhance your style with our cap featuring a slight curved visor. Designed for a modern look and comfortable wear, perfect for everyday use.</li><li>STITCHING: Elevate your style with our cap featuring a pro-stitched finish and contrast stitching on neon/black and neon/graphite colorways. Designed for durability and visual appeal, this cap is perfect for active lifestyles and casual wear.</li><li>CLOSURE: Adjustable for a perfect fit, our snapback cap combines style with comfort. Featuring a snapback closure, it ensures versatility and ease of wear for any occasion.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-3\">Options and add-ons from the live Distributor Central product page for this SKU. Pricing may change; confirm on your quote.</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50/30\">\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Apparel Color and Size</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] f